CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page 16, reads: "2. Huge crowds filled every inch of available space in exhibit hall"
TitMainTitle: Women, including one standing on right wearing light colored hat and dark short sleeve blouse with lace cuffs, holding shopping bag, gathered around curved staircase in Syria Mosque for the 1956 Courier Home Service Fair
